(2, 2016, 'sample4.pdf', '2023-12-07 13:08:56', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(129, 138, 162); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni Fun Club is a unique concept. The objective is to promote fun and joy at campus and connect all JGEC passport holders across the globe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(129, 138, 162); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni association exist to support specific goals, and to strengthen the ties between alumni, students, the community, administration and JGEC as a whole.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(129, 138, 162); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni Association appeals entire established alumnus of our beloved alma mater to promote organized sporting and cultural events inside campus to promote extracurricular activities. The purpose is to promote leadership, group activities, individual and group excellence, morale building and fun.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(129, 138, 162); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni Association appeals sponsors of various schemes under Alumni Fun Club to continue (respective schemes) at least for 5 years as minimum from its year of inception. However if it gets discontinued within above mentioned period due to any emergency reason from Sponsor&#39;s side, then Alumni Association shall not remain responsible for that act of discontinuity.</p>', '[\"1703681402_1703053736.jpg\"]');
