(17, 'kanchenjunga', '', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&quot;Kanchenjunga&quot; the state-of-art convention centre in the heart of JGEC campus, has been conceptualized by the Alumni Association and a dream in making. Named after the mystic mountain which has been a source of inspiration for all of us in our life, it will comprise of a seminar cum conference hall with technologically advanced video conferencing facilities, meeting rooms, knowledge sharing room, library along with a reading room and guest rooms.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	As the largest, most comprehensive and accessible convention centre in the JGEC campus; it is planned to be an ecologically sensitive building contributing towards our beloved Institute and Mother Nature. It is conceived to promote innovativeness among the JGEC fraternity. With its sophisticated and technologically advanced facilities, Kanchenjunga would be a natural choice of the industry and the corporates for their business summits, seminars and workshops in North Bengal. With generous contributions of the Alumni, the land to build Kanchenjunga has been purchased. Construction of the Annex facility of the convention centre is under advanced stages of implementation.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		A long awaited home for our college alumni is coming up in a bought out private land just behind the mechanical workshop of our JGEC. It is taking shape by the active financial and other support from our students&nbsp; present and past.Besides the three storied building alone. The Alumni is actively involved in providing support to the needy student population in&nbsp; the surrounding&nbsp; area and helping current JGEC students reaching for number of sponsored scholarships offered from outside.</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Going back to Kanchanjangha, the ground floor is operational already. Several functions have been held in the auditorium and the hall. Recently the first floor roof have been casted and the interior work is under progress. Bathroom tiles fitted.</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		It is a great achievement by the alumni members there and of course by the financial support from the members community. The remaining part which is the 2nd floor is only awaiting to view the real beauty of the world famous Kanchanjanhha.</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		To achieve this Alumni needs much needed financial support. May we request that whoever&#39;s is coming across this call to please&nbsp; contribute,&nbsp; however small it may be in the designated bank account regularly shared in the website of the association.</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'admin', '2017-08-30 14:34:01', 1),
(18, 'kanchenjunga', 'An Insight of Project Kanchenjunga', '<h4>\r\n	Locational Advantage</h4>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Project Kanchenjunga is located inside the premises of Jalpaiguri Government Engineering College campus, which is located at Jalpaiguri district town of West Bengal. Since it is located near Jalpaiguri town, which is a well-known administrative and tourist town in northen part of West Bengal, it would enjoy several locational advantage. The district economically is driven by the revenues and employment generated by sprawling tea gardens of the Dooars, agricultural products and forest resources. Established in 1980, Siliguri- Jalpaiguri Development Authority (SJDA) is a nodal agency for the development of the area. SJDA is in process of developing a modern Industrial Estate and a major satellite township. Several entrepreneurs have recently expressed their keenness in setting up agro and food based industries in the nearby areas. The place is well connected by road (NH 34), rail (2kms from Jalpaiguri road station) and the nearby airport (Bagdogra) is at a distance of about 55 kms.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni Association has purchased a parcel of private land inside JGEC campus premises for Project Kanchenjunga.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<h4>\r\n		Amenities and Facilities</h4>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Fully equipped conference cum seminar hall with video conferencing facilities</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Meeting and Discussion Rooms</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Knowledge Sharing Rooms and workstations</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Reading room facilities with Mini Library</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			5 to 6 Air Conditioned Guest Rooms</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Pantry</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Open Terrace</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Photo copiers, Wifi connectivity, Power back up</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Ownership and Institutional Structure</h4>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Kanchenjunga&#39;s ownership lies with the Jalpaiguri Government Engineering College Alumni Association. Over the years, JGEC has produced many leaders, entrepreneurs, managers, qualified engineers and professionals who collectively have abundance of knowledge and experience. The Alumni Association established in 2010 brings all these talented &amp; outstanding individuals. Project Kanchenjunga is likely to become one of threads connecting all such brilliant minds and driven by the motto &quot;Driven by Gratitude, Bonded with Nostalgia&quot;. This is an effort in a view of contributing to the growing generation, the Institute and the society as a whole.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		With a gamut of experts from their field of specialization, it&#39;s evident that the Association is adept to nurture, design, execute and operate Kanchenjunga.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Project Cost and Schedule</h4>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		The estimated cost of Kanchenjunga is INR 2 crores (INR 20 million) at current prices. Please refer folder &quot;Financial Model&quot;.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Considering a regular fund flow, the project is scheduled to be completed in its entirety by 2018. Alumni Association requests sponsors and contributors for their active financial support till Kanchenjunga&#39;s successful completion.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Sustainability of Kanchenjunga</h4>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		A corpus fund shall be kept for maintenance of Kanchenjunga. Apart from that, the sustainability of Kanchenjunga can be ensured by organizing seminars, workshops and value based programs on a regular basis.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Contributing towards the Cause</h4>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Kanchenjunga is located within the premises of the prestigious Jalpaiguri Government Engineering College, the premier Institute in North Bengal. It is constructed and will be operated by professionals and reputed experts from the Alumni Association. Conceptualized to be one of the state-of-art convention centre in entire North Bengal, Kanchenjunga is likely to attract industry and corporate leaders not only from the region but also from the State. Apart from organizing regular seminars and workshops, Alumni Association foresees opportunities to offer Kanchenjunga and its services to corporate houses for business summits, meetings and seminars. This will generate a regular revenue stream and ensure its self-sustainability. Kanchenjunga will have 5 to 6 furnished guest rooms for accommodation.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Whether your hairs are grey with years of experience or you are a rising star spearheading ambitious missions of your life, whether you stay connected with your JGEC buddies or you are missing your old chaps in the daily rush of busy life, your JGEC still remains your very own Alma Mater! Yes, Kanchenjunga is that dream which can give you back all those Nostalgia and the precious moments that you miss today and soon will be a reality for you and the proud JGECians across the globe. Please come forward, contribute towards this great cause to make it a success.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Alumni Association is also engaged in consulting with institutional sponsors and corporate to garner support for Kanchenjunga.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		How to Contribute for Kanchenjunga</h4>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Online Money Transfer through www.jgecalum.org</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Transferring money to Alumni Association&#39;s SBI current account (at Danguajhar Branch) as follows:</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		SBI C.A. Account No. 31232430610</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		IFSC Code: SBIN0007194</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\">Note: Any contribution to Alumni Association is exempted under 80G [as per letter from the Office of the Commissioner of Income Tax (Exemptions)</span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'admin', '2017-08-30 14:35:22', 1),
(30, 'upcoming-events', 'Message from President Desk', '<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Respected Senior, My Dear Friends and Beloved Brothers &amp; Sisters,</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">I am thankful to all that you have trusted me to serve my beloved alma mater as President of the Alumni Association.</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">I am not confident, and I do not want to be that I will be able to guide the association with innovation &amp; vision for success; rather I believe that, until and unless you all perform, it is impossible to lead such a prestigious platform.</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">I hope, all of you will take an active part with your ideas and activities. The verticals or sub-committees are formed by Alumni Association which can perform successfully only of all of you take active participation in Alumni initiatives.</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">I shall remain busy in housekeeping only which is essential to run such an active and growing organization.</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The decision will be a process of harnessing participation from all of you (starting from the governing body to vertical members, senior alumni who guide us as mentors, members of Alumni Association and every alumnus of our beloved alma mater). We will work in close coordination with our Respected Principal Sir, our Respected Professors. We will be humble to all of the stakeholders of our beautiful alma mater.</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Our motto should be to accept new ideas having relevance to the present scenario &amp; future vision. I hope you all will be active to guide our future generations.</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Yours faithfully,</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mr. Bhaskar Dasgupta</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">(1979-1983)</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n', 'admin', '2018-01-09 10:49:43', 1),
(31, 'upcoming-events', 'Appeal for Kanchenjunga', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(62, 63, 58); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; background-color: rgb(248, 245, 240);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Alumni Association is pleased to inform you all that the first floor construction has been completed and outside painting is going to start. All are cordially invited for the grand opening of our dream house &quot;Kanchenjunga&quot; on 7th August, 2022. Your presence is most welcome during the inauguation program.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgb(62, 63, 58); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 245, 240);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Alumni Association requests all respected alumnus to contribute to build Kanchenjunga...it&#39;s all about DREAM and realization of the Dream.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	Here is the details to contribute for Kanchenjunga (a Convention Centre inside JGEC Campus):<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	Recipient Name: The Jalpaiguri Government Engineering College (JGEC) Alumni Association<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	Address: JGEC Campus, P.O. Denguajhar, Dist. Jalpaiguri, PIN - 735102, West Bengal, India</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgb(62, 63, 58); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 245, 240);\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">SBI C.A. Account No. 31232430610<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	IFSC Code: SBIN0007194<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	Branch Code: 7194</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgb(62, 63, 58); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 245, 240);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thanks to All of You.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgb(62, 63, 58); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(248, 245, 240);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">22-05-2022</span></p>\r\n', 'admin', '2018-01-09 10:53:25', 1),
(32, 'bulletin', 'Scholarship Day', '<div>\r\n	After a rigorous process involving all the stakeholders (students, alumnus and college authority and sponsors), it&#39;s time to close the Scholarship Program 2023.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The list of Scholarship Recipients are published today.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Sponsors have came into conclusion after lots of deliberation. Many scholarships are provided based on financial requirements and some are provided considering overall performance of a students, as per selection criteria set by sponsors.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Alumni Association scholarship program started in 2013 with four students and this year scholarship are provided to 43 students.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	We wish all the best to the Scholarship Recipients. Also, we would like to stay beside to our beloved brothers and sisters who are not selected this year.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	We wish more scholarships schemes to be added in future so that we can support more students.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Best wishes from the JGEC Alumni Association, JGEC Campus, Jalpaiguri, WB, India.</div>\r\n', 'admin', '2019-09-06 09:23:41', 1),
