unga Inaugurated</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					Alumni Association purchased an available private land inside JGEC campus for Kanchenjunga (Convention Centre, Alumni House &amp; Students development Centre)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:114px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					August</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					2016</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:264px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					Inauguration of Annexed Facility of Kanchenjunga &amp; Alumni Temporary Office;</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					Celebration of Golden Jubilee of Graduation of 1<sup>st</sup> Batch of JGEC Alumnus</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:114px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					February</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					2017</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:264px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					Launch of Intra College Innovation Challenge &ndash; in collaboration with Centre for Innovation</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					(Motivating innovation &amp; entrepreneurial leadership amongst students)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:114px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					July</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					2018</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:264px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					Beginning of Experience Sharing Welcome Sessions with the first-year students</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					(Since 2018, Alumni Association participate in this annual event)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:114px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					December</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					2020</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:264px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					Completion of Ground Floor of Kanchenjunga (Phase-I)&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n					(Next Target is to complete next Phases for first &amp; second floors, and enhance value added activities at campus with more Alumni-Students &amp; Professor&rsquo;s Engagements)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'admin', '2020-09-28 02:15:17', 1),
(55, 'giving-back', 'Commitment for Our Beloved Alma Mater', '<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>It&#39;s All About DREAM</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Jalpaiguri Government Engineering College Alumni Association got registration on 22nd day of April 2010&nbsp;from Registrar of Societies West Bengal Act XXVI of 1961</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;vide No:-S/L/70053</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;of 2010-11</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. Alumni Association functions from College Administrative Building.</span></h2>\r\n<h1>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 11px;\">SYSTEM DRIVEN MECHANISM</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Since inception at JGEC Campus, Alumni Association is continuously trying to provide value based organised alumni activities at campus. Also, it is dedicatedly working to enhance JGEC Brand through regular activities. Today scientists, industry leaders, top professors, HoDs and directors of different IITs come to campus at least twice a year, which we never thought off earlier. Alumni Association organises regular workshops for students, creative programs for Centre for Innovation and scholarship programs. Alumni Association has channelized alumni effort into systematic approach. Of course, miles to go.</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 11px;\">BRIDGING THE GAP</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Students are backbone behind formation of Alumni Association. Despite various tough situation, alumni association has become successful at campus only because of students of JGEC. Previously, there was no organized alumni effort to provide exposure to students and promote brand JGEC. After formation of alumni association at our beloved JGEC campus, Bridging the Gap initiative started on a regular and routine basis.</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 11px;\">KANCHENJUNGA</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">During regular activities, AA has assessed situations inside campus. Student&rsquo;s orientation, professor&rsquo;s feedback, market scenario etc have been assessed and it was decided that there should be a sustainable effort which can provide global exposure to students and promote brand JGEC.</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Despite of our 60 years history, unfortunately we are not as strong brand as we supposed to be. Assessing the situation and how much alumni association can implement in reality effectively (so that our contribution should not be wasted), Alumni Association (AA) has decided to go for a self-sustainable model, Kanchenjunga (a G+2 knowledge centre and convention centre). It should be a brand which shall make entire JGEC fraternity proud.<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Please join the initiative to &nbsp;Build Kanchenjunga : a tribute to our beloved Alma Mater</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">You can contribute in fund drive initiative as well:</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">A/C Name: <strong>Jalpaiguri Govt. Engineering College Alumni Association</strong>, </span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">SBI - Current A/C no - <strong>31232430610</strong>, </span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">IFSC - <strong>SBIN0007194</strong>, </span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">MICR - 735002512.</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0.5in;\">SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM ACTIVITIES</span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0.5in;\">The sponsors provide the scholarship by using the Alumni Association platform. Every year, Alumni Association organizes scholarship orientation program. Alumni Association website provides the scholarship opportunities to JGEC students where students apply for the scholarship online. Alumni Association organizes the scholarship program and interview/ sorting mechanism in consultation with the sponsors. Number of students are selected based on their documented financial and academic records. Face-to-face interview session also arranged to provide career developmental experience to the students. Also, career development guidance provided to the students during scholarship orientation program. In 2020 &amp; 2021, online interview sessions were organized during COVID-19 pandemic time. Sponsors provide the scholarship amount to the students either through Alumni Association or direct payment to the deserving students.</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">First sentence To be corrected as -- :</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Scholarship Program is getting organised in Campus via face toface interview since 2013 in a proper documented manner .</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;To encourage innovative ideas, Alumni Association organized Innovation Challenge inside JGEC campus, every year two times, along with Centre for Innovation. Most importantly students connect themselves with alumni activities. All these possible due to thrust for quality which is encouraged by all the ex-students of JGEC.</span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<strong style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px;\">INDUSTRY ACADEMIA INTERACTION</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">For last ten years, the Jalpaiguri Government Engineering College Alumni Association (having HQ inside JGEC campus) has continually working towards achieving excellence, with dedicated set of engineers, through Bridging the Gap events.</span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">In these nine years, two directors of IIT visited campus to attend seminar organised by alumni association (Dr. C V R Murthy and Dr. Gautam Biswas). President of Indo American Chamber of Commerce visited campus in addition to academicians/ industry persons and successful ex-students (such as Dr. Promode Bandyopadhyay - ASME Award Winner Scientist from Naval Undersea Warfare Centre USA, Professor Ashok Kumar Moulik and so on).</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">CONCEPT TO COMMISSIONING</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Before taking decision for Kanchenjunga (state of the art Convention Centre), AA had various options to do something for JGEC in an organized way. But AA had decided a path which can make some positive impact to campus and society as a whole. Concept notes, SWOT analysis were few approaches which had been adopted during feasibility study. Alumni Association&#39;s objective is to incorporate values to the system by providing positive inputs to our students to face larger life and at the same time building Brand JGEC which can highlight JGEC&rsquo;s contribution towards Industry &amp; society. Long run consideration (with the bigger interest to serve our Alma Mater and thus serve society via a systematic structured platform with a social commitment to add value to our Alma Mater) and planning is embedded in this Project (commonly known as PK Project Kanchenjunga) and it is built on commitment.</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you want to be part of this social commitment, please join the initiative as it suits you.</span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">It&#39;s all about DREAM and Realisation of the Dream</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 11px;\">Driven by Gratitude, Bonded with Nostalgia</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">27-05-2022</span></span></h2>\r\n', 'admin', '2020-09-28 14:43:44', 1);
