(56, 'giving-back', '', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Am I Taking a Right Decision?</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The most challenging question which confound a student when deciding the institute to suit their needs is &quot;where should I study?&quot; Universities, Colleges and Schools have just mushroomed all over within the past decades worldwide. Students have plenty of choices when choosing the one.<br />\r\n	With everyone offering the best of syllabus, faculty and infrastructure, Alumni connect have become a strategic asset for any kind of higher education institution willing to stand out from the domestic and international competition.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">STRATEGIC ASSET</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Alumni Connect is a Strategic Asset</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">This means that&hellip;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;An institution&rsquo;s alumni are the reflection of its past, symbol of its present and a connection to its future.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Educational institutions are shifting the way they interact with their alumni community.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Earlier, alumni and their a</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">lma-mater were treated as discrete entities wherein one&rsquo;s existence was independent of the other.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Local alumni chapters at different locations away from the institute used to form as a means to interact with other fellow alumni. However, these associations seldom had any interaction with the institution. That&#39;s the reasons institutions globally are focusing for centralised campus-based Alumni platform.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">With the advent of Social Media and digital technology, alumni relationship has taken a different flavour altogether. Centralised alumni platform of institutions have started to harness the power of alumni through various networking platforms and focusing on connecting ex-students with campus.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">MOST LOYAL AMBASSADOR &nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">There are various ways in which alumni association is creating a powerful impact to campus because alumnus are most loyal ambassador of the campus.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Support system</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">An engaged alumni network allows the University to benefit from the skills and experience of our graduates, by offering their support to our students, to the institution and to each other. If we keep them well informed and engaged, alumni are our most loyal supporters and our best ambassadors, offering invaluable marketing and promotion across their personal and professional networks.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Of</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">fering expertise</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Talented alumni will likely have a treasure of experience and skills to share with current students via talks and meets. In certain cases, this could go even further with alumni offering to practically support students in work placements and help them launch their careers.&nbsp;&nbsp; JGEC Alumni Association has&nbsp;created an engaged alumni network which is beneficial because engaged graduates are much more likely to want to &ldquo;give back&rdquo; to the beloved alma mater. During COVID pandemic, JGEC Alumni Association successfully introduced webinar platform where alumni across the globe got an opportunity to interact with the student in real-time.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Mentorship</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Alumni can play an active role in voluntary programs like mentoring students in their areas of expertise. JGEC Alumni Association has created a structured platform where students got opportunity, through Bridging the Gap initiative, to interact with successful alumnus, professionals, academicians and scientists at JGEC campus. Also through Innovation Challenge, students can nurture and showcase their talents on a regular intervals.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Scholarship</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Alumnus also play a significant role in contributing scholarships to deserving students. Alumni get in touch with students and share their expertise and best practices in a given field.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Assistance in Employability</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Alumni Association&#39;s function is not to create job. But Alumni Association helps to connect alumnus with campus and create alumni network. Alumni network has a real-life benefit for current students. Alumni also donate their valuable time to offer career support to current students. This enhances the students&rsquo; experience and give them that competitive edge in today&rsquo;s tough job market.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">For JGEC Alumni Association, focus is beloved JGEC Campus and close interaction with students. Alumni Connect is one of the biggest strengths for JGEC and Alumni Association is committed to enhance the Brand JGEC.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">East or West, JGEC is the Best.</span></strong></em></span></p>\r\n', 'admin', '2020-09-28 15:11:44', 1),
(57, 'bulletin', 'SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM 2023', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		Interested brothers and sisters are suggested to apply for Scholarship Schemes by 25th June, 2023.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Link for application:&nbsp;<strong>https://jgecalum.org/scholarship</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Our Respected Alumnus and their Respected Family Members have come forward to stay beside our brothers and sisters by using the platform created by Alumni Association.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		The unique and innovative online Scholarship Program is part of Bridging the Gap initiative created by Alumni Association, which was showcased by our beloved institute during NAAC Audit process (which is documented under the NAAC tab of JGEC official website). The 1:1 interview process is part of the students counselling and knowledge sharing process where our Respected Alumnus and Sponsors used to share their vast experiences with engineering students.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>Important Features of Scholarship Program 2023:</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		1. Total no. of Scholarship Schemes:&nbsp;<strong>26</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		2. No. of students to benefitted through the Scholarship Program:&nbsp;<strong>44</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		3. Total Scholarship Amount: Approximately&nbsp;<strong>Rs.7,28,000/-</strong>&nbsp;(Rs. Seven Lacs Twenty Eight Thousands only)</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>Schedule for the Scholarship Program 2023:</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		1) Opening date of application by students of JGEC:&nbsp;<strong>11</strong><strong><sup>th</sup></strong>&nbsp;<strong>June, 2023</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		2) Last date of application by students of JGEC:&nbsp;<strong>25<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;June, 2023</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		3) Selection of top three candidates by sponsors:&nbsp;<strong>5<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;July, 2023</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		4) Interview of top 3 candidates (optional) by sponsors:&nbsp;<strong>5<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;August, 2023</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		5) Scholarship Award Day:&nbsp;<strong>6<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;August, 2023 (Sunday).</strong></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Note: All applications will be considered for 2023 -&#39; 24 academic year only.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'admin', '2021-07-07 11:13:16', 1),
(58, 'upcoming-events', 'JGEC ALUMNI SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM 2023', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Important Features of Scholarship Program 2023</strong><strong>:</strong></span></div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1. Total no. of Scholarship Schemes: <strong>27</strong></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2. No. of students to benefitted through the Scholarship Program: <strong>46</strong></span></div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				&nbsp;</div>\r\n			<div>\r\n				<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. Total Scholarship Amount: Approximately <strong>Rs.7,49,000/-</strong> (Rs. Seven Lacs Forty Nine Thousands only)</span></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Interested brothers and sisters have applied for the Scholarship Schemes for 2023 and the 1:1 interview &amp; processing is underway, with active participation of Respected sponsors, beloved JGEC students and Respected Professors.&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Link for scholarship: <strong>https://jgecalum.org/scholarship</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Scholarship sponsors also have provided their information in the above link.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Alumni Association convey sincere regards to all the individual sponsors (Alumnus of JGEC and/ or their family members) and batches (like 1996, 1999, 2002 and 2004) for standing beside financially challenged and/ or meritorious students of JGEC.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">With best wishes from</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The JGEC Alumni Association</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">JGEC Campus, Jalpaiguri</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">WB, India</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Driven by Gratitude, Bonded with Nostalgia</strong></span></div>\r\n', 'admin', '2021-08-13 23:56:13', 1),
(59, 'take-a-trip', 'WHERE SHALL I STUDY?', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Am I Taking a Right Decision?</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	The most challenging question which confound a student when deciding the perfect Institute to suit their needs is &quot;where should I study?&quot; Universities, Colleges and Schools have just mushroomed all over within the past decades worldwide. Students have plenty of choices when choosing the best and most promising one. With everyone offering the best of syllabus, faculty and infrastructure, Alumni connect have become a strategic asset for any kind of higher education institution willing to stand out from the domestic and international competition.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>STRATEGIC ASSET</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni Connect is a Strategic Asset. This means that&hellip;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		An institution&rsquo;s alumni are the reflection of its past, representation of its present and a link to its future.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Educational institutions are changing the way they see and interact with their alumni community.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Earlier, alumni and their alma-mater were treated as separate entities wherein one&rsquo;s existence was independent of the other.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Local alumni chapters were formed as a means to interact with other fellow alumni. However, these associations seldom had any interaction with the institution they graduated from. That&#39;s the reasons institutions globally are focusing for centralised campus based Alumni platform.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		With the advent of Social Media, alumni relationship has taken a different flavour altogether. Centralised alumni platform of institutions have started to harness the power of alumni through various networking platforms and focusing on connecting ex-students with campus.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Most Loyal Ambassador&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	There are various ways in which alumni association is creating a powerful positive impact to campus because alumnus are most loyal ambassador of the campus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Support S</strong><strong>ystem</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	An engaged alumni network allows the University to benefit from the skills and experience of our graduates, by offering their support to our students, to the institution and to each other. If we keep them well informed and engaged, alumni are our most loyal supporters and our best ambassadors, offering invaluable marketing and promotion across their personal and professional networks.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Offering Expertise</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Talented alumni will likely have a wealth of experience and skills to share with current students via talks and meets. In certain cases, this could go even further with alumni offering to practically support students in work placements and help them launch their careers.&nbsp; &nbsp;JGEC Alumni Association has&nbsp; created an engaged alumni network which is beneficial because engaged graduates are much more likely to want to &ldquo;give back&rdquo; to the University.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Mentorship</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni can play an active role in voluntary programs like mentoring students in their areas of expertise. JGEC Alumni Association has created a structured platform where students got opportunity, through Bridging the Gap initiative, to interact with successful alumnus, professionals, academicians and scientists at JGEC campus. Also through Innovation Challenge, students can nurture and showcase their talents on a regular intervals.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Scholarship</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumnus also play a significant role in contributing scholarships to deserving students. Alumni get in touch with students and share their expertise and best practices in a given field.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Assistance in Employability</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Alumni Association&#39;s function is not to create job. But Alumni Association helps to connect alumnus with campus and create alumni network. Alumni network has a real life benefit for current students. Alumni also donate their valuable time to offer career support to current students. This enhances the students&rsquo; experience and give them that competitive edge in today&rsquo;s tough job market. The alumni network of a college is one of the biggest sources of placement opportunities to the students. Alumni can help students get placed at their respective organizations.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Why Alumnus Like to Connect?</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Leveraging the alumni community through campus based initiatives is a win-win for both the institution and the alumni. Many of them are willing to &lsquo;Give-Back&rsquo; to their alma-mater as a sign of their gratitude and affinity towards the institution.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Reconnect.</strong> Find and reminisce with fellow graduates; see what everyone&rsquo;s been up to!</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Give back.</strong> Make meaningful connections, recruit future Wildcats, speak to students and advise fellow alumni.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Expand.</strong> Leverage your professional network to get introduced to people you should know.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Advance.</strong> Advance your career through inside connections who work at top companies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'admin', '2021-08-14 00:01:46', 1),
(60, 'upcoming-events-home', 'SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM - 2023', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Interested brothers and sisters are suggested to apply for Scholarship Schemes by 25th June, 2023.</span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Link for application:&nbsp;<strong>https://jgecalum.org/scholarship</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<h2>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Our Respected Alumnus and their Respected Family Members have come forward to stay beside our brothers and sisters by using the platform created by Alumni Association.</span></span></h2>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The unique and innovative online Scholarship Program is part of Bridging the Gap initiative created by Alumni Association, which was showcased by our beloved institute during NAAC Audit process (which is documented under the NAAC tab of JGEC official website). The 1:1 interview process is part of the students counselling and knowledge sharing process where our Respected Alumnus and Sponsors used to share their vast experiences with engineering students.</span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Important Features of Scholarship Program 2023:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. Total no. of Scholarship Schemes:&nbsp;<strong>27</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. No. of students to benefitted through the Scholarship Program:&nbsp;<strong>46</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. Total Scholarship Amount: Approximately&nbsp;<strong>Rs.7,49,000/-</strong>&nbsp;(Rs. Seven Lacs Forty Nine Thousands only)</span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Schedule for the Scholarship Program 2023:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">1) Opening date of application by students of JGEC:&nbsp;<strong>11</strong><strong><sup>th</sup></strong>&nbsp;<strong>June, 2023</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">2) Last date of application by students of JGEC:&nbsp;<strong>25<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;June, 2023</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">3) Selection of top three candidates by sponsors:&nbsp;<strong>5<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;July, 2023</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">4) Interview of top 3 candidates (optional) by sponsors:&nbsp;<strong>5<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;August, 2023</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">5) Scholarship Award Day:&nbsp;<strong>6<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;August, 2023 (Sunday).</strong></span></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Note: All applications will be considered for 2023 -&#39; 24 academic year only.</span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'admin', '2021-08-16 09:42:06', 1),
